OL,3,CRayner calls for Burnham's return and
OL,4,Cwarns Starmer needs to 'set out change'
OL,6,FAngela Rayner has called on Sir Keir
OL,7,FStarmer to "set out the change our
OL,8,Fcountry needs" as she warned Labour is
OL,9,Ffacing its "last chance" after a
OL,10,Fdisastrous set of election results.
OL,12,FThe former deputy leader and Ashton-
OL,13,Funder-Lyne MP, widely seen as a
OL,14,Fpotential successor to the Prime
OL,15,FMinister, stopped short of calling for
OL,16,Fhim to quit but set out a series of
OL,17,Fsteps he needed to take to win back
OL,18,Fworking-class voters.
OL,26,@oD@LOUpD@NO]qD@LOUqD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
