PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778523070
OL,3,CRayner calls for Burnham's return and
OL,4,Cwarns Starmer needs to 'set out change'
OL,6,FShe added that it had been a mistake
OL,7,Fto block Andy Burnham's possible
OL,8,Freturn to Westminster, saying Labour
OL,9,Fneeds to bring its "best players into
OL,10,FParliament".
OL,12,FGreater Manchester mayor Mr Burnham is
OL,13,Falso seen as a potential rival to Sir
OL,14,FKeir, but his attempt to stand in the
OL,15,FGorton and Denton by-election was
OL,16,Fthwarted by Labour's hierarchy.
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
