FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778523070
OL,3,CRayner calls for Burnham's return and
OL,4,Cwarns Starmer needs to 'set out change'
OL,6,FIn a 1,000-word assessment of what
OL,7,FLabour needs to do, Ms Rayner said:
OL,8,F"What we are doing isn't working, and
OL,9,Fit needs to change. This may be our
OL,10,Flast chance."
OL,12,FIn England, Nigel Farage's Reform UK
OL,13,Fsnatched councils, some of which had
OL,14,Fbeen Labour for generations, in
OL,15,Fnorthern England while Zack Polanski's
OL,16,FGreen Party lured voters away in
OL,17,Fformer urban strongholds, including
OL,18,Ftaking control of some London
OL,19,Fauthorities.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@MO]
