OL,3,CRayner calls for Burnham's return and
OL,4,Cwarns Starmer needs to 'set out change'
OL,6,FIn Wales, Labour was reduced from the
OL,7,Fparty in government to a single-figure
OL,8,Frump in one of its former heartlands.
OL,10,FMs Rayner said: "In London, we lost
OL,11,Fyoung people who fear they will never
OL,12,Fafford a home. In my patch and across
OL,13,Fthe north, we lost working people
OL,14,Fwhose wages are too low and costs too
OL,15,Fhigh. In Scotland and Wales, people do
OL,16,Fnot currently see Labour as the answer.
OL,18,F"We are in danger of becoming a party
OL,19,Fof the well-off, not working people."
OL,26,@rD@QOUzD@AOU{D@eO]
