OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778523070
OL,3,CRayner calls for Burnham's return and
OL,4,Cwarns Starmer needs to 'set out change'
OL,6,FMs Rayner said: "Policy tweaks will
OL,7,Fnot fix the fundamental challenges
OL,8,Ffacing our country. This Government
OL,9,Fneeds, at pace, to put measures in
OL,10,Fplace that make people's lives
OL,11,Ftangibly better, while fixing the
OL,12,Ffoundations of a system rigged against
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,F"The Prime Minister must now meet the
OL,16,Fmoment and set out the change our
OL,17,Fcountry needs.
OL,26,@nD@QOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
