PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1778523070
OL,3,CRayner calls for Burnham's return and
OL,4,Cwarns Starmer needs to 'set out change'
OL,6,F"Change our economic agenda to
OL,7,Fprioritise making people better off,
OL,8,Fchange how we run our party so that
OL,9,Fall voices are listened to, and change
OL,10,Fhow we do politics.
OL,12,F"Labour exists to make working people
OL,13,Fbetter off. That is not happening fast
OL,14,Fenough, and it needs to change ` now."
OL,16,FMs Rayner quit as deputy leader and
OL,17,Fdeputy prime minister last September
OL,18,Fafter failing to pay the correct tax
OL,19,Fon a flat in Hove.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@fO]
